The Talon is the daily news broadcast of the students at Eagleview Middle School. It is a student run broadcast. Students perform all the duties from running the cameras and sound board to being anchors.
Broadcasts are filmed during the morning and aired to the school in the afternoon.
&nbsp;
Students are on a rotation through the news studio.
